1
00:00:09,384 --> 00:00:10,636
Look familiar?

2
00:00:10,844 --> 00:00:11,803
No.

3
00:00:12,179 --> 00:00:13,347
Me either.

4
00:00:13,472 --> 00:00:15,557
I do not believe I have been to this planet before.

5
00:00:15,599 --> 00:00:18,519
There's no sign of any settlements,
or at least nothing recent.

6
00:00:18,810 --> 00:00:21,480
Other than the smoke from that camp fire.

7
00:00:24,858 --> 00:00:25,776
Oh,

8
00:00:25,817 --> 00:00:27,069
yes well,

9
00:00:27,361 --> 00:00:28,612
other than that.

10
00:00:30,989 --> 00:00:33,408
I'll land within a few hundred yards

11
00:00:48,382 --> 00:00:50,592
It's primitive, definitely primitive.

12
00:00:50,926 --> 00:00:53,011
Probably not even worth making contact.

13
00:00:53,470 --> 00:00:54,888
What is that smell?

14
00:00:59,768 --> 00:01:04,106
- It appears they left in a hurry.
- They're not used to friendlies coming out of the Gate.

15
00:01:06,775 --> 00:01:07,818
<i>What are you?</i>

16
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:12,072
Oh my God, he's tasting it!
You don't know what that is.
That could be their laundry!

17
00:01:13,031 --> 00:01:14,157
Pretty good.

18
00:01:15,492 --> 00:01:20,289
Oh yes, good idea. And when you're finished
with their porridge, why don't we try their beds.

19
00:01:21,582 --> 00:01:22,624
Want some?

20
00:01:23,876 --> 00:01:26,587
- How good is it?
- Leave it be Goldilocks.

21
00:01:31,049 --> 00:01:32,426
<i>Take cover!</i>

22
00:01:45,689 --> 00:01:47,816
<i>What the hell's in those sling shots?</i>

23
00:01:52,946 --> 00:01:53,947
You alright?

24
00:01:54,156 --> 00:01:55,199
Fine!

25
00:01:58,994 --> 00:02:02,164
You know this is not
the way to make new friends!

26
00:02:04,291 --> 00:02:06,793
But we'll leave if you want us to!

27
00:02:09,171 --> 00:02:12,382
I'll take that as a yes.
Let's go back to the Jumper. Teyla you're on point.

28
00:02:12,508 --> 00:02:15,093
- I'll take the six. McKay help Ronan.
- Don't worry about me.

29
00:02:15,135 --> 00:02:17,971
I'm a worrier. Let the man give you a hand.

30
00:02:20,516 --> 00:02:21,683
Fire!

31
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:02,766
Alright move, move!!

32
00:03:22,286 --> 00:03:24,663
- Everyone in one piece?
- Yeah, thanks to that ship.

33
00:03:24,705 --> 00:03:25,873
Be still.

34
00:03:26,290 --> 00:03:27,708
Yeah, I like their timing.

35
00:03:27,749 --> 00:03:30,252
- No kidding, you see that thing?
- Yeah, I saw that thing.

36
00:03:30,502 --> 00:03:31,670
<i>Unidentified ship.</i>

37
00:03:31,712 --> 00:03:36,508
<i>This is the security vessel Borus.</i>
<i>Follow us immediately and we will lead you to the city.</i>

38
00:03:36,925 --> 00:03:38,093
<i>Understood Borus.</i>

39
00:03:38,385 --> 00:03:40,053
<i>Thanks for the help back there.</i>

40
00:03:40,846 --> 00:03:43,265
That's how you make new friends.

41
00:03:50,355 --> 00:03:53,525
Transcript:
Callie Sullivan & Scifigate.net

42
00:03:53,567 --> 00:03:56,737
Subtitles by Team SG-66
